---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---
<section id="about">
  <div class="container about-grid">
    <div class="about-text reveal from-left">
      <p class="section-label">About Antoni</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Your Florida Real Estate Expert</h2>
      <span class="line-draw"></span>
      <p>For over two decades, I have been helping buyers, sellers, and investors navigate the greater Tampa Bay real estate market. As a REALTOR® with <a href="https://gocrr.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-link">Charles Rutenberg Realty</a>, I've built a career on honest advice, meticulous attention to detail, and an unwavering commitment to my clients' best interests.</p>
      <p>I specialize in <strong>first-time homebuyers</strong> and <strong>real estate investors</strong> alike. I take the time to inspect every home we tour and am always upfront about concerns — because your long-term satisfaction matters more than a quick sale.</p>
      <ul class="about-creds stagger">
        <li><span class="cred-dot"></span>21+ Years at Charles Rutenberg Realty</li>
        <li><span class="cred-dot"></span>Licensed Florida REALTOR®</li>
        <li><span class="cred-dot"></span>Investment Property Specialist</li>
        <li><span class="cred-dot"></span>First-Time Homebuyer Specialist</li>
        <li><span class="cred-dot"></span>Greater Tampa Bay Market Expert</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="about-actions">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Work With Me</a>
        <a href="https://gocrr.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-ghost">Charles Rutenberg Realty</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-image reveal from-right">
      <img src={`${base}/headshot.png`} alt="Antoni D. Marinov, REALTOR®" />
      <div class="about-badge">
        <span class="badge-num">21+</span>
        <span class="badge-text">Years in Tampa Bay</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #about { background: var(--white); }
  .about-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 80px; align-items: center; }

  .about-text p { color: #4B5563; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 0.97rem; }
  .about-text strong { color: var(--navy); }
  .text-link { color: var(--gold); font-weight: 600; border-bottom: 1px solid currentColor; }
  .text-link:hover { opacity: 0.75; }

  .about-creds { list-style: none; margin: 24px 0 32px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 9px; }
  .about-creds li { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-size: 0.92rem; font-weight: 500; }
  .cred-dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--gold); flex-shrink: 0; }

  .about-actions { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn-ghost { color: var(--navy); border-color: #D1D5DB; }
  .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--navy); box-shadow: none; }

  .about-image {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: visible;
    transition-delay: 0.15s;
  }
  .about-image img {
    width: 100%; border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    display: block;
  }
  .about-badge {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 24px; right: 32px;
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--white);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }
  .badge-num { display: block; font-size: 1.9rem; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1; }
  .badge-text { font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; opacity: 0.9; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
    .about-text { order: 2; }
    .about-image { order: 1; }
  }
</style>
